OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FIn just a few days, the FIFA World Cup
OL,7,F2026 will begin, giving football fans
OL,8,Fthe chance to see all of their
OL,9,Ffavourite, big-hitting teams and
OL,10,Fplayers.
OL,12,FBut with a new format featuring 48
OL,13,Fcountries, there is also space for new
OL,14,Fteams to emerge, surprises to unfold,
OL,15,Fand unlikely winners to make their
OL,16,Fmark on the global stage.
OL,18,FFrom first-time qualifiers to the
OL,19,Fsmallest nations breaking records, ITV
OL,20,FNews breaks down the underdog teams to
OL,21,Fwatch.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
