OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,F1. Cape Verde
OL,8,FPlaying at its first-ever World Cup,
OL,9,FCape Verde is already making history.
OL,11,FThe former Portuguese colony is an
OL,12,Farchipelago in the Atlantic islands
OL,13,Fthat has a population of little more
OL,14,Fthan half a million people.
OL,16,FWhen the team qualified for the
OL,17,Ftournament in October last year, many
OL,18,Flocals said it was the biggest thing
OL,19,Fto happen to Cape Verde since it
OL,20,Fgained independence on July 5, 1975.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
