OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781395390
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FAt the time, head coach Pedro Brito
OL,7,FLeao, also known as "Bubista", told
OL,8,Fthe BBC: "Giving this happiness to
OL,9,Fthese people is enormous.
OL,11,F"It's a special moment in this
OL,12,Fcelebration of the 50th anniversary of
OL,13,Four independence."
OL,15,F2. Uzbekistan
OL,17,FAnother country to qualify for the
OL,18,FWorld Cup for the first time is the
OL,19,Fformer Soviet state, Uzbekistan which,
OL,20,Fonly 10 years ago, was ruled by a
OL,21,Frepressive authoritarian regime.
OL,26,@oD@Ctp
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
