OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FThe team became the first Central
OL,7,FAsian country to participate in the
OL,8,Ftournament after a 0-0 draw in Abu
OL,9,FDhabi.
OL,11,FOne of its star players is the 22-year-
OL,12,Fold central defender Abdukodir
OL,13,FKhusanov, who plays for Manchester
OL,14,FCity.
OL,16,FHe is the product of a recent - and
OL,17,Fseemingly successful - push by the
OL,18,FUzbek government to get more people
OL,19,Finvolved in football.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
