OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FIn 2022, it announced it would open
OL,7,Fdozens of government-funded youth
OL,8,Ffootball academies as well as 3,500
OL,9,Fmini football fields across the
OL,10,Fcountry.
OL,12,FFootball has been hugely popular in
OL,13,FUzbekistan, but watching their team
OL,14,Fplay at a World Cup will be a
OL,15,Fhighlight for many locals.
OL,17,F3. Curacao
OL,26,@yD@H{q
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
