OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FWith a population of only 158,000
OL,7,Fpeople Curacao is the smallest ever
OL,8,Fnation ever to qualify for a FIFA
OL,9,FWorld Cup.
OL,11,FThe tiny Caribbean island, which has a
OL,12,Fland area of only 171 square miles,
OL,13,Fhas several star players who play in
OL,14,Fthe UK, including Middlesbrough winger
OL,15,FSontje Hansen and Sheffield United's
OL,16,FTahith Chong.
OL,18,FThe Caribbean island nation certainly
OL,19,Fhave their work cut out in Group E,
OL,20,Fwhere they will face Germany, Ecuador,
OL,21,Fand Cote d'Ivoire.
OL,26,@oD@L{q}D@Fsw
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
