OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FThe team will be well managed under
OL,7,Fthe 2026 tournament's oldest head
OL,8,Fcoach, Dutchman Dick Advocaat, who is
OL,9,F78 years old.
OL,11,F4. New Zealand
OL,13,FDespite making its third appearance in
OL,14,Fthe tournament, the New Zealand 'All
OL,15,FWhites' have never won a World Cup
OL,16,Fmatch or made it to a knock-out round.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
