OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FThey were the only unbeaten team in
OL,7,Fthe 2010 FIFA World Cup - by drawing
OL,8,Fall three group stage games - but they
OL,9,Ffailed to advance to the knockout
OL,10,Fstage.
OL,12,FThe team's captain, Chris Wood, plays
OL,13,Fas a forward for Nottingham Forest and
OL,14,Fhas returned to full fitness in time
OL,15,Ffor his second World Cup.
OL,17,FDefender Tim Payne also shot to social
OL,18,Fmedia fame in May, after an Argentine
OL,19,Finfluencer wanted to promote what he
OL,20,Fcalled the World Cup's "least-known"
OL,21,Fplayer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
