SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781395390
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FValen Scarsini, known as 'elscarso'
OL,7,Fonline, shared an Instagram video
OL,8,Fcalling on his followers to follow
OL,9,FPayne.
OL,11,F"I looked at all the teams that play
OL,12,Fthe World Cup for the least-known
OL,13,Fplayer and, after analysing one by
OL,14,Fone, I found it," Scarsini said in a
OL,15,Fvideo that has more than six million
OL,16,Fviews.
OL,18,F"Tim Payne is a defender and has a
OL,19,Fvery difficult task: help New Zealand
OL,20,Fwin their first World Cup match. They
OL,21,Fhave never won one."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
