OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FPunters believe the team has an
OL,7,Fopportunity to reach the knockouts for
OL,8,Fthe first time.
OL,10,FWhile Belgium will be a difficult
OL,11,Ffirst match for them, the 'All Whites'
OL,12,Fmay have a chance of beating Egypt and
OL,13,FIran in the group stages.
OL,15,FHaiti is among the five lowest-ranked
OL,16,Fteams in the tournament and is
OL,17,Fcompeting for only the second time in
OL,18,Fits history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
