OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FThe team, which includes star captain
OL,7,FDuckens Nazon, secured its spot
OL,8,Fwithout playing a single qualifying
OL,9,Fgame on home soil.
OL,11,FA travel ban introduced by the Trump
OL,12,Fadministration last year, means most
OL,13,FHaitian fans will not be able to get a
OL,14,Fvisa to enter the US.
OL,16,FHowever, there are around 852,000
OL,17,FHaitian immigrants already living in
OL,18,Fthe country, according to the latest
OL,19,Ffigures.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
