OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FStill, fans have complained that they
OL,12,Fwon't be able to support their team in
OL,13,Fperson due to the expensive tickets.
OL,15,F"For a long time, my office have been
OL,16,Fadvocating for community tickets at a
OL,17,Flow cost or no cost, and we have just
OL,18,Fhit walls every time," Haitian-
OL,19,FAmerican Boston City Councillor
OL,20,FRuthzee Louijeune told Al Jazeera.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
