OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1781395390
OL,3,CFIFA World Cup 2026: Who are the
OL,4,Cunderdogs?
OL,6,F"I know there are Haitian people that
OL,7,Fare going, that have purchased tickets
OL,8,Fat face value, or whatever price is
OL,9,Fgoing on online, but it is cost-
OL,10,Fprohibitive for a number of people in
OL,11,Four community."
OL,13,FThe team will face Brazil, Morocco and
OL,14,FScotland in one of the tournament's
OL,15,Ftoughest groups.
OL,17,FThe FIFA World Cup 2026 will run from
OL,18,FJune 11 to July 19, 2026.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
